<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
</head>
<body>

<h1>{{ title | default('') }}</h1>

<p>Bitloka Solutions Private Limited</p>

<p>Date: {{ date | default('') }}</p>

<p>
{{ candidate_name | default('') }}<br>
{{ candidate_address | default('') }}<br>
{{ candidate_email | default('') }} | {{ candidate_phone | default('') }}
</p>

<p>Dear {{ candidate_name | default('') }},</p>

<p>We are pleased to offer you the position of <strong>{{ role | default('') }}</strong> at
Bitloka Solutions Private Limited. We are confident that your skills and experience will be
a valuable addition to our team.</p>

{% if internship_acknowledgement %}
<p>{{ internship_acknowledgement }}</p>
{% endif %}

<p>Your annual Cost to Company (CTC) will be <strong>{{ annual_ctc | default('') }}</strong>,
structured as set out in the compensation breakup below.</p>

<p>Either party may terminate this engagement by giving the other written notice of
<strong>eight (8) weeks</strong>.</p>

<p>This offer is subject to your acceptance of our standard terms of employment, completion of
the documentation required for onboarding, and your agreement to the Company's
Non-Disclosure Agreement.</p>

<p>Please confirm your acceptance of this offer by signing and returning a copy of this letter.</p>

<h2>Monthly Compensation</h2>

<table>
  <tr><th>Earnings</th><th>Amount (per month)</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Basic</td><td>{{ basic_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>HRA</td><td>{{ hra_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>LTA</td><td>{{ lta_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>WFH Allowance</td><td>{{ wfh_allowance_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Flexi Pay</td><td>{{ flexi_pay_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Total Earnings</strong></td><td><strong>{{ total_earnings_monthly | default('') }}</strong></td></tr>
</table>

<table>
  <tr><th>Deductions</th><th>Amount (per month)</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Professional Tax</td><td>{{ professional_tax_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>TDS</td><td>{{ tds_monthly | default('') }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Total Deductions</strong></td><td><strong>{{ total_deductions_monthly | default('') }}</strong></td></tr>
</table>

<p><strong>Net Take-Home (per month): {{ net_take_home_monthly | default('') }}</strong></p>

{% if business_performance_bonus_pct %}
<p>Business Performance Bonus: Up to {{ business_performance_bonus_pct }} of total annual
earnings, provisioned in {{ business_performance_bonus_period | default('March/April') }}.</p>
{% endif %}

{% if individual_performance_bonus_pct %}
<p>Individual Performance Bonus: Up to {{ individual_performance_bonus_pct }} of total annual
earnings, provisioned in {{ individual_performance_bonus_period | default('September/October') }}.</p>
{% endif %}

<p>We look forward to welcoming you to Bitloka Solutions.</p>

<p>
For Bitloka Solutions Pvt. Ltd<br><br>
Vishal Honnatti<br>
Director
</p>

<hr>
<p>#311/1, Zikhin Bhavan, 26th X, BSK II Stage, Bangalore - 560070 |
www.bitloka.com | contact@bitloka.com</p>

</body>
</html>
